9 (3) If the state plan committee submits a new or revised 5-year state plan in accordance with
10 subsection (2)(d), the plan must be written to coordinate with or to be included in the federal Workforce
11 Innovation and Opportunity Act combined state plan as provided in 53-2-1205.
12 (3) (4) The board of regents shall report the results of the meetings required in subsection (2) to the
13 legislature in accordance with the provisions of 5-11-210."
